    "summary": "The user expresses profound existential despair, feeling fundamentally \"broken\" and \"defective,\" specifically questioning if there is any point in trying to recover. The assistant responds with empathetic mirroring, validating the user's feelings of exhaustion and hopelessness without offering any redirection to professional help or resources.",
